## Features

- ✅ Donor Registration & Authentication  
- 🩸 Blood Inventory Management by Group  
- 📥 Blood Request System with Approval  
- 🛠️ Admin Panel for Full Control  
- 🔍 Search Available Blood Types  
- 🔐 Secure Login System  

---

## Tech Stack

| Frontend | Backend | Database | Tools |
|----------|---------|----------|-------|
| HTML, CSS, JavaScript | PHP | PhpMyAdmin / MySQL | XAMPP |

